"Scatterseed\n"
"Deeproot\n"
"Scryer’s Bloom\n"
"Thorntress\n"
"Summit Star\n"
"Kindlefire\n"
"Stillseed\n"
"Reaper’s Moon\n"
"Verglas Bloom\n"
